BULGARIA: Bulgaria offers 2.2 bln levs discount bills on Wed.Bulgaria offers 2.2 bln levs discount bills on Wed.Bulgaria's Finance Ministry will offer a special issue of 2.2 billion levs worth of 34-day discount T-bills at an auction on Wednesday, the Bulgarian National Bank (BNB) said.Settlement for the auction will be made on Thursday, August22, at the average accepted price.Details of the issue follow: Issue number	BG 3015996005 Par value	   2.2 billion levs Auction date	August 21, 1996 Issue date	  August 22, 1996 Maturity date     September 25, 1996-- Sofia Newsroom, (++359-2) 981 8569